# Wholesale Central Changelog - Development Rules

## Project Overview

This is the changelog website for Wholesale Central, a B2B eCommerce platform connecting wholesalers with retailers since 1997. The site is built with Next.js and MDX.

## Adding New Changelog Entries

When new changes need to be documented, follow these steps:

### 1. Add Entry to `src/app/page.mdx`

Add new entries at the TOP of the file (below the imports), following this format:

```mdx
---

![](@/images/your-image-name.png)

## Entry Title {{ date: 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' }}

Brief description of what changed and why it matters to users.

### <SparkleIcon /> Bug Fixes

- Fixed [issue description]
- Resolved [issue description]

### <SparkleIcon /> Improvements

- Added [feature description]
- Enhanced [improvement description]

### <SparkleIcon /> New Features

- Introduced [new feature]
```

### 2. Adding Images

1. Place changelog images in `src/images/`
2. Use descriptive names: `feature-name.png`, `bug-fix-overview.png`
3. Recommended image dimensions: 1200x630px (16:9 aspect ratio)
4. Reference images using: `![](@/images/your-image.png)`

### 3. Date Format

Always use ISO 8601 format: `YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ`
Example: `2024-12-02T00:00Z`

### 4. Entry Categories

Use these SparkleIcon sections as needed:
- **Bug Fixes**: For resolved issues and errors
- **Improvements**: For enhancements to existing features
- **New Features**: For completely new functionality
- **Breaking Changes**: For changes that require user action (use sparingly)

### 5. Writing Style

- Write from the platform's perspective (use "we" or passive voice)
- Keep descriptions concise but informative
- Focus on user impact, not technical details
- Use present tense for what the change does
- Link to documentation when relevant: [Learn more](https://learn.wholesalecentral.com)

## Environment Variables

Required environment variables for email subscriptions:

```env
POSTMARK_SERVER_TOKEN=your-postmark-server-token
POSTMARK_FROM_EMAIL=changelog@wholesalecentral.com
POSTMARK_NOTIFY_EMAIL=team@wholesalecentral.com (optional)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://changelog.wholesalecentral.com
```

## File Structure

```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── api/
│   │   └── subscribe/     # Email subscription API
│   ├── feed.xml/          # RSS feed
