├── components/
│   ├── Intro.tsx          # Hero section with links
│   ├── Logo.tsx           # Wholesale Central logo
│   ├── SignUpForm.tsx     # Email subscription form
│   └── ...
├── images/                # Changelog entry images
└── styles/
```

## Brand Guidelines

- Primary brand color: #EDAB2F (Wholesale Central gold)
- Text on dark: #050E40 (dark blue)
- Keep the existing color scheme - only update content
- Logo files: `logo_dark_bg.svg` (for dark backgrounds), `logo_light_bg.svg` (for light)

