## Sending Update Emails

When a significant changelog entry is added, use Postmark to notify subscribers:

1. Create a template in Postmark for changelog updates
2. Include entry title, date, and summary
3. Link back to the full changelog

## Testing Locally

```bash
npm run dev
```

Visit http://localhost:3000 to preview changes.

## RSS Feed

The RSS feed at `/feed.xml` automatically includes all changelog entries. No manual updates needed.

